title: Camco (40055) RV Brass Inline Water Pressure Regulator- Helps Protect RV Plumbing and Hoses from High-Pressure City Water
description: Camco Brass Water Pressure Regulator helps to protect the RV and boat plumbing and hoses from damage caused by high-pressure city water. Reduce water pressure to a safe, consistent 40–50 PSI of operational pressure. Protects appliances, plumbing fixtures, and prevents hose failure, to help prolong equipment life. Female garden hose (3/4 - 11-1/2 NH) x male garden hose (3/4 – 11-1/2 NH). Patented. For outdoor use only.
